com.neebal.android.simplyreliable.message

Class MessageDependency

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.neebal.android.simplyreliable.message.MessageDependency
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class MessageDependency
extends Object
implements Serializable
    A wrapper class that represents a Message instance that a particular Message instance may be dependent upon before it can be sent to the server and whether the Message instance's dependency is fullfilled or no. It also includes ways in which the current Message instance can be updated, whenever the Message that it depends upon has its dependency fulfilled
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Neebal Technologies
